{"tid":1665123,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［正視聽］罷食紅茶到底有冇錯？","createTime":"2019-10-20T12:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T03:14:19.000Z","uid":221968,"like":26,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"428d916e4c5e77fa941e46b6ef4582282a49a83b","tid":1665123,"uid":221968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7BezxZL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7BezxZL.jpg&h=96d8b605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你人哋唔係藍㗎<br />\n唔割蓆 但道歉同幫人清潔返啦好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事緣就有ching開個post屌手足噴字罷食係錯，但多名巴打都見過員工屌手足（已FC,包括我自己），但又有人聲稱佢哋借廁所，員工罷工。而事實係佢冇試過加藤屋式罷工。<br />\n<br />\n咁為正視聽，唯有開個post比各方澄清，有冇實質證據證明 紅茶唔係藍/紅。<br />\n<br />\n如果有，大家再一齊道歉。始終大家再爭論都冇用，留待紅茶正面回總好過冇止境又冇意義的爭論。"},{"pid":"eb9caac0227667118db5591c9a5b080729ec70fb","tid":1665123,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"佐敦紅茶，長期播CCTVB新聞"},{"pid":"81d129003e5deab45168f2bdadd19aec74f540d2","tid":1665123,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"老闆有冇鬧手足？"},{"pid":"6e7e37d18492ae0822d534fd742ef28e842f902d","tid":1665123,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾紅茶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd6907ebf392156f4cb2d5107d547b4b298fdf4","tid":1665123,"uid":128472,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"藍黃待確認 但我覺得藍既都唔需要裝修，粉飾下就ok"},{"pid":"f87dc66d0a12de680b964b5aeda8b0a136b8bcc1","tid":1665123,"uid":24265,"like":49,"dislike":4,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"eb9caac0227667118db5591c9a5b080729ec70fb","tid":1665123,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"佐敦紅茶，長期播CCTVB新聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老